<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Excluir Policial</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Excluir Policial</h1>
    <p>Tem certeza que deseja excluir o policial <strong><%= policial.nome %></strong> (Matrícula: <%= policial.matricula %>)?</p>
    <form action="/policiais/remover/<%= policial._id %>" method="POST">
        <button type="submit">Confirmar Exclusão</button>
        <a href="/policiais/relatorio">Cancelar</a>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
